name: libvoikko
description: Compiled from [libvoikko](https://github.com/voikko/corevoikko/tree/master/libvoikko) with [emscripten](https://emscripten.org/). Single file build with Finnish language dictionary [Joukahainen](https://joukahainen.puimula.org/) included. Currently only [morpho](https://www.puimula.org/htp/testing/voikko-snapshot-v5/) dictionary is included.
